    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to a standard that transcends the typical secondary market offering. This unit is in pristine condition, exhibiting a flawless exterior profile and an interior that retains its original factory integrity. Every mechanical component has been rigorously vetted to ensure peak performance, offering the discerning collector or enthusiast an experience indistinguishable from a new delivery. This is an investment-grade asset for those who demand uncompromising quality and aesthetic perfection.",
