      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolutely pristine condition\u2014seriously, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It\u2019s been pampered since day one and runs like a total dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the sticker shock, this is the one for you! Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 43500.0,
